items.title: Italian journalist Cecilia Sala freed by Iran
items.description: Reports said Sala had been held in solitary confinement in Tehran's notorious Evin prison.

items.title: ChatGPT creator denies sister's childhood rape claim
items.description: Ann Altman filed a lawsuit alleging her brother sexually abused her between 1997 and 2006.

items.title: US accuses Sudanese paramilitary of genocide and sanctions its leader
items.description: The paramilitary group is accused of the "systematic" murder of men and boys and brutal sexual violence.

items.title: Trump ramps up threats to gain control of Greenland and Panama Canal
items.description: The president-elect said he would not rule out the use of military force to seize control of the Panama Canal and Greenland.

items.title: Timelapse shows rapid spread of Palisades wildfire
items.description: A plume of smoke is seen billowing over Los Angeles in a video charting the wildfire's growth.
